    Config
    Main Configuration structure in Constant Contact.
    Config.Auth
    OAuth2 Authorization related configuration options.
    Config.COLUMN_NAMES
    Collumn names in Constant Contact Activities flow.

    These are used for ExportContactsRequest and .components.activities.contacts.request.AddContactsRequest requests in BulkActivitiesService.
    Config.Endpoints
    Contains a list with all REST endpoints.
    Config.Errors
    Errors to be returned for various exceptions in the Constant Contact flow.
    Config.HTTP_CODES
    HTTP Return Codes in Constant Contact flow.
    Config.Login
    Login related configuration options in Constant Contact.
    These are used for the login part of the authentication flow.
